data.description: Enjoy a $2,000 seller incentive towards rate buy down or closing cost concession! Step into this captivating two-story home boasting curb appeal. Impeccably maintained with freshly painted interiors, it awaits new owners. The well-designed floor plan and inviting ambiance make for comfortable living. The heart of the home is the spacious island kitchen, featuring dark cabinetry, granite countertops, and a unique backsplash. The formal dining space offers versatility for a living area, playroom, or home office. The main floor primary ensuite is a tranquil retreat with dual sinks, a tub, and a separate shower. Upstairs, a generous loft and bonus room provide space for your entertainment dreams. Outside, an expansive patio with a fire pit is perfect for gatherings. This former model home boasts upgraded features such as double barrier windows for a quiet interior, a fully finished garage with heating and cooling, and prewired speakers. Convenience is key with the central vacuum system.
